3) [u]The End of Marriage?[/u]

More and more men and women are choosing not only to marry later in life, but not marrying at all.  What does this mean for the institution of marriage?  How is this changing gender relations at home and in the workplace?  And does this mark the end of marriage, or signal the start of new types of partnerships?

